	* compilers/gcc/: BUILD, CONFIGURE, DETAILS, POST_INSTALL,
	lunar-g++, lunar-gcc: Updating gcc module:
	  Builds in external dir.
	  Installs lunar wrappers for gcc and g++ (lunar-gcc and lunar-g++).
	  Creates symbolic link from cc to lunar-gcc instead of gcc.
	  Enables ccache, distcc, and -pipe (as well as others) to work.
	  Enables many modules to compile that did not before.
	  Enables reccomened compile option (--enable-__cxa_atexit).
	  Uses bootstrap-lean to compile smaller and faster (less resources needed).
	
